snippet: Australia will head into the Boxing Day test against Pakistan unchanged from the side that closed out a nerve-jangling 39-run win in the first match in Brisbane on Monday....
lead_paragraph: Australia will head into the Boxing Day test against Pakistan unchanged from the side that closed out a nerve-jangling 39-run win in the first match in Brisbane on Monday.
